{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a9bf54fae","title":"如平敌撤退则志愿军向三八线攻进","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fee5619bb0","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"7a9bf54fae"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7826a16eaa","type":"title","text":"如平敌撤退则志愿军向三八线攻进！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"},{"id":"edcc5080bd","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、邓、朴、洪，并告高、贺，宋、陶","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"},{"id":"c95c5e4594","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）平故似正准备撤退。（二）请派出几个有力侦察队附电台道近镇南浦、平、三登之线进行威力侦察，观察情况，并增加故人热悦。该敌现在一夕数惊，极为热悦。（三）请指定人民军一个三千至五千人的师及党政人员位于接近平地点，准备于查明故人确已撤退时进平维持秩序。（四）我志愿军休息五大后，如平故未退则准备先打平现附近之故，然后包围平，研究攻城办法。如平敌已退，则向三八线攻进。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"},{"id":"e4b59e7f31","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"},{"id":"f7c6d1b492","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月四日十三时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"},{"id":"a3c720f9b7","type":"paragraph","text":"I这是毛泽东给中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀，副司令员兼副政治委员邓华、朴一禹，副司令员洪学智的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae"}],"page":{"id":"e8dd7beff2","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a9bf54fae","start":418,"end":418}}}},"__N_SSG":true}